## Responsive Navigation Patterns

### 1. Hamburger Menu

```html
<nav class="navbar">
  <button class="menu-toggle" aria-expanded="false">
    <span class="sr-only">Menu</span>
    ☰
  </button>
  
  <ul class="nav-menu">
